To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private StandardDeviation _std;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_std = STD(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_std.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "standarddeviation", _std.Current.Value);
}
